Description: Provides transparent, contract-first infrastructure for
    Bayesian analysis of repeated-measures and hierarchical behavioural
    data. It supports explicit data and model contracts, readiness audits,
    deterministic simulation, inspectable prior specifications, diagnostic
    assessment, sensitivity analysis, and conservative reporting for
    approved model families. Optional Bayesian backends are not required
    for package installation or core validation.
